<p>I am able to get the value of itemname only if that row is focused , but  i need the value for all the rows from list which are not in focus also</p>  <pre><code> public View getView(final int position,View convertView, final ViewGroup parent){      View view = convertView;      final ViewHolder holder;       if(view == null){         LayoutInflater inflater = mContext.getLayoutInflater();         view = inflater.inflate(R.layout.additemlistitems_row, null);          holder = new ViewHolder();             holder.itemname  = (TextView)view.findViewById(R.id.itemname);             holder.itemname.setTag(list.get(position));          view.setTag(holder);      } else {         view = convertView;              holder = (ViewHolder) convertView.getTag();          ((ViewHolder) view.getTag()).itemname.setTag(list.get(position));      }      Log.d("ListAdapter","ItemName - &gt; "+list.get(position).ItemName);      return view; }    </code></pre>